            <description><![CDATA[【一道隔夜菜，65岁大爷肝功能“爆表”，全身发黄！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】65岁的谢大爷（化名）独自在深圳过年，怕浪费，吃了一周剩菜后，开始拉肚子。之后，开始觉得恶心、浑身没力气、肚子胀，吃不下东西。一周后，谢大爷的精神愈发萎靡，全身皮肤变得很黄，眼睛也发黄，尿液变成浓茶色，大便却是白陶土色！到医院一查，谢大爷肝功能指标通通“爆表”！谢大爷被诊断为急性黄疸型戊型病毒性肝炎，是实打实的“病从口入”！👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%2365%E5%B2%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%B7%E8%BF%9E%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%89%A9%E8%8F%9C%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%E5%8F%91%E9%BB%84%23&amp;extparam=%2365%E5%B2%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%B7%E8%BF%9E%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%89%A9%E8%8F%9C%E5%85%A8%E8%BA%AB%E5%8F%91%E9%BB%84%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#65岁大爷连吃一周剩菜全身发黄#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc7ghivak9j20mv0mjahp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc7ghknjrqj20v980ub29.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc7ghlnhh9j20v98tke81.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc7ghn1ixwg20t40ja7wj.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
